2. Description of the Service

Pocketful is a creative journaling app that runs entirely on your device. In this version of the App, you can:

Capture photos, audio, text, and doodles as “stickers”

Arrange these elements into visual cards and collections (“tin boxes”)

Create and organize multiple themed collections on your device

All features in the current version of Pocketful are provided free of charge.
There are no in-app purchases, no subscriptions, and no paid premium features in this version.

The App does not require you to create an account and does not connect to any backend server for your content.

We may update or change features in future versions, but any major change (such as adding paid features or accounts) would be reflected in updated Terms and Privacy Policy.

3. User Content
3.1 Ownership

You retain all rights to the content you create in Pocketful, including:

