Text notes and reflections

Drawings and doodles

Cards and collections

We do not claim ownership of your content.

3.2 Storage

Your content is stored locally on your device only.
We do not upload your creative content to our servers, because we do not operate a content backend for Pocketful.

Because we do not host your content:

We cannot access, view, or modify what you create in the App

We cannot restore your data if it is lost or deleted on your device

If you choose to share your creations (for example via screenshots or system share sheet), that sharing happens through your device and the apps you choose, not through our servers.

